CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, August 11, 1945, pg. 13, reads: "Jr. Frogs - After a 'jump' session.  Left to right: Doris Nunn, Tommy Cromm [Croom], John Thompson, Marilyn Ware, William Battles, Marguerite Dodson, Harold Penn, Sylvania [Sylvia] Calloway and Mozelle Thompson.  The Junior Frags are a group of young Pittsburgh men soliciting the sponsorship of the Frogs.  They hope to merge with the thirty-six-year-old original group. - All Photos By Harris."
TitMainTitle: Marilyn Ware (Parker) kneeling in center, with Doris Nunn, Tommy Croom, John Thompson, William Battles, Marguerite Dodson standing in front, and John Cannon, Sylvia Calloway, Harold Penn, and Mozelle Thompson in back row, in South Park lodge for FROGS picnic
